description: Solidus is a limitless eCommerce platform. Create an integrated experience that has your brand's style all over it.
---

<div class="use-cases-hero hero-block content-block--skewed content-block-white pb-0">
  <div class="content-wrapper">
    <div class="content-block pt-0">
      <nav class="subnav">
        <ul class="container">
          <small>Use Cases</small>
          <li class="subnav__item selected">
            <a class="subnav__item__link" href="#">Online Stores</a>
          </li>
          <li class="subnav__item">
            <a class="subnav__item__link" href="#">Headless commerce</a>
          </li>
          <li class="subnav__item">
            <a class="subnav__item__link" href="#">Marketplace</a>
          </li>
          <li class="subnav__item">
            <a class="subnav__item__link" href="#">Global commerce</a>
          </li>
          <li class="subnav__item">
            <a class="subnav__item__link" href="#">Omnichannels</a>
          </li>
          <li class="subnav__item">
            <a class="subnav__item__link" href="#">B2B</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-lg">
          <div class="pr-lg-6 mb-3">
            <h5>Online Stores</h5>
            <h1 class="title">Supercharge <span class="d-block">your store.</span> Amaze your customers.</h1>
            <p class="mb-6">
              Choose a limitless eCommerce platform. Create an integrated experience that has your brand's style all over it.
            </p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact">Get started</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-white" href="http://solidemo.herokuapp.com/" target="_blank">Demo</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg">
          <div class="hero-image-wrapper">
            <img data-srcset="<%= image_path('use-cases/online-stores_hero@2x.png') %> 2x, <%= image_path('use-cases/online-stores_hero@1x.png') %> 1x" class="img-fluid" alt="Online Stores" >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="intro content-block--skewed content-block-gray-100 pb-0">
  <div class="content-wrapper">
    <div class="content-block pt-0">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="lead text-gray-600 text-center font-weight-light mb-4">
          Solidus powers the brands defining the future of eCommerce.
        </p>
        <%= partial "partials/community_logos" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="use-cases__image col-md">
          <img src="<%= image_path("use-cases/online-stores_01@1x.png") %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path("use-cases/online-stores_01@2x.png") %> 2x, <%= image_path("use-cases/online-stores_01@1x.png") %> 1x" class="img-fluid" width="100%" alt="Content-first commerce" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-md">
          <div class="use-cases__header">
            <h5>Content-first commerce</h5>
            <h2>Tell your story, win their hearts.</h2>
          </div>
          <p>
            Connecting with your customers is key to building a successful brand, and there's nothing better than storytelling for doing that. Integrate with any headless CMS to create inspirational content. Static pages, blog posts, different media and formats — there’s nothing you can't do. Create a 360-degree experience that turns visitors into lifelong fans.
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="btn-link">Link</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content-block">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="use-cases__image col-md order-md-2">
            <img src="<%= image_path("use-cases/online-stores_02@1x.png") %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path("use-cases/online-stores_02@2x.png") %> 2x, <%= image_path("use-cases/online-stores_02@1x.png") %> 1x" class="img-fluid" width="100%" alt="Omnichannel" />
          </div>
          <div class="col-md">
            <div class="use-cases__header">
              <h5>Omnichannel</h5>
              <h2>Use new channels in new ways.</h2>
            </div>
            <p>
              Digital brands don't just sell through their store: social media, brick and mortar, marketplaces, mobile apps… We know you will constantly experiment with new channels, and we want to give you and your customers an amazing experience. Wherever you want to be, Solidus has got your back with powerful logistics, marketing and reporting integrations.
            </p>
            <a href="#" class="btn-link">Link</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="use-cases testimonials">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <div class="carousel-content">
      <div class="main-image-container">
        <img src="<%= image_path("use-cases/case-study_yearandday@1x.jpg") %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path("use-cases/case-study_yearandday@2x.jpg") %> 2x, <%= image_path("use-cases/case-study_yearandday@1x.jpg") %> 1x" class="img-fluid" width="100%" alt="Year&Day" />
      </div>
      <div class="blockquote-container">
        <blockquote class="blockquote yearandday d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
          <a class="logo" href="https://yearandday.com/" target="_blank"><%= inline_svg("community-logos/yearandday.svg", class: "isvg") %></a>
          <div>
            <%= inline_svg("icons/quote.svg", class: "quote") %>
            <p class="pl-4">
              If you love the joy baked into the Ruby programming language and need to sell products, Solidus should be on the forefront of your radar. Thoughtful refactoring goes into the codebase daily, the community is exceptionally friendly and building a product that sells goods couldn't be easier.
            </p>
          </div>
          <footer class="blockquote-footer pt-3">
            <cite>
              <img src="<%= image_path("community-logos/o-vazquez.png") %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path("community-logos/o-vazquez@2x.png") %> 2x, <%= image_path("community-logos/o-vazquez.png") %> 1x" class="img-circled" width="48" height="48" alt="Lorem Ipsum" />
              <span class="text">
                <span class="author">Lorem Ipsum</span>
                  Developer at Year&Day
                </span>
              </cite>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content-block">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="use-cases__image col-md">
      <img src="<%= image_path("use-cases/online-stores_03@1x.png") %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path("use-cases/online-stores_03@2x.png") %> 2x, <%= image_path("use-cases/online-stores_03@1x.png") %> 1x" class="img-fluid" width="100%" alt="Custom storefront" />
      </div>
      <div class="col-md">
        <div class="use-cases__header">
          <h5>Custom storefront</h5>
          <h2>Make your storefront truly yours.</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
          Forget about themes and templates: your brand doesn't fit the mold. Personalize your entire checkout flow, create upselling and cross-selling opportunities, build complex taxonomies that let users explore your products from different angles, and whatever else you need to build the shopping experience your customers deserve.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-link">Link</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content-block">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="use-cases__image order-md-2 col-md">
      <img src="<%= image_path("use-cases/online-stores_04@1x.png") %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path("use-cases/online-stores_04@2x.png") %> 2x, <%= image_path("use-cases/online-stores_04@1x.png") %> 1x" class="img-fluid" width="100%" alt="Reporting" />
      </div>
      <div class="col-md">
        <div class="use-cases__header">
          <h5>Reporting</h5>
          <h2>Use data like never before.</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
          There’s no one-size-fits-all when it comes to analytics, but most eCommerce platforms leave you stuck with their default reports. Solidus lets you retain full ownership over your data: build custom reports right in your store’s backend, or connect your store to external reporting and analytics tools for even more advanced use cases. It’s your brand — why shouldn’t it be your data?
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-link">Link</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

